=Episode 21=
(Boundaries Crossed, Chains Undone)

12
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,710
Let part of the army into the city

13
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:01,030
to guard the general's mansion

14
00:01:01,350 --> 00:01:03,600
and have another battalion on standby.

15
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:05,560
