17
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:09,840
With Duan Xunrui's death,

18
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,790
Duan Xunchu will certainly take revenge.

19
00:01:12,230 --> 00:01:13,680
But he fears our strength,

20
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:16,120
so he will not act blindly for now.

21
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,070
Other than taking precautions,

22
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,280
it looks like we need to strike first.

23
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:23,430
Understood.

24
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:25,870
Who is it?

25
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,280
It's me.

26
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,510
Come in.

27
00:01:34,230 --> 00:01:34,870
Excuse me, Miss.

28
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,350
My dear girl,

29
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,680
do you have something to tell me?

30
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:41,150
Dad,

31
00:01:41,790 --> 00:01:43,400
he might be your adopted son

32
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,790
but he didn't commit any heinous crime.

33
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,430
